  "description": "The image depicts a high-voltage power line against a clear, bright blue sky. The power line consists of multiple black cables suspended by a series of orange, disc-shaped insulators. Above the cables is a complex network of metal support structures, forming a tower or pylon. The structure is constructed of interconnected triangular metal beams, creating a geometric and industrial aesthetic. The insulators are prominently displayed and contribute a strong visual contrast to the blue sky and dark cables. The angle of the shot emphasizes the repeating pattern of the insulators and the vastness of the power infrastructure.",
